author: Tom FitzGerald
title: Keller Chryst blocks out space as Stanford’s backup QB
text:
Photo: Marcio Jose Sanchez, Associated Press Stanford quarterback Keller Chryst was 4-of-4 passing for 39 yards and a touchdown against Arizona on Saturday. Stanford quarterback Keller Chryst was 4-of-4 passing for 39 yards...
All that head coach David Shaw will say about Stanford’s backup-quarterback competition is that it’s “fluid.” But it was clear as of the Arizona game that Keller Chryst has won the duel with Ryan Burns for the No. 2 spot.
